<h2 class="head-font arti-head">Taweaways</h2>
<div class="content-arti-clean flex flex-around flex-end">
    <div class="content-arti-copy">
        <p>This project was humbling in that I needed to critically examine complex shapes and colours, and find ways to slowly build them up using simpler shapes and layered gradients. Through this project, I found that vectors can be an incredibly powerful tool, and can accomplish visual complexity, opening vectors up as both a creative and nuanced tool for design.</p>
